BRIEFING: CLOUDS AND SHOWERS ASSOCIATED WITH THE DIMINISHING FRONT WILL CONTINUE TO IMPACT PORTIONS OF MAUI COUNTY THIS MORNING THEN PORTIONS OF THE BIG ISLAND THROUGH THE DAY AS IT DRIFTS EASTWARD. SHOWERS WILL MOSTLY FAVOR SW THRU N FACING SLOPES, WITH THE LOW-LEVEL FLOW GRADUALLY VEERING FROM THE WSW TO THE N THROUGH THE DAY. ELSEWHERE EXPECT DRIER CONDITIONS TO FILL IN FROM W TO E BEHIND THE FRONT.
SENTRY ALOHA JAN 29 - FEB 12 NO MILITARY SCHEDULED
